OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly fine in this period, however
OL,7,Fthe easterly breeze is likely to bring
OL,8,Fspells of low cloud. Often eventually
OL,9,Fbrightest in the west after generally
OL,10,Fcloudy, chilly starts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
